1. There are many Operators used in C programming Languages

2. Operator Tools are of 6 types
    
    1) Arithmetic +, -, *, /, %
    2) Relational Operator >, <, >=, <=, ==
    3) Logical &&, ||, !
    4) Assignment operator =, +=, -=, *=, /=, %=
    5) sizeof operator
    6) Bitwise operator &, |

3. incrementation of a value of a variable is of two types:
    ++ is the operator used incrementation.
    There are two types
    post incrementation, pre incrementation 

4. decrementation of a value of a variable is of two types:
    -- is the operator used decrementation.
    There are two types
    post decrementation, pre decrementation 